Someone's here.

00:13:25.260 --> 00:13:26.500
I threw up a lot.

00:13:26.500 --> 00:13:27.380
I think it's related to my age...

00:13:27.380 --> 00:13:27.980
Dr. Li.

00:13:28.500 --> 00:13:29.420
Dr. Li is here.

00:13:29.420 --> 00:13:29.780
Miss?

00:13:29.780 --> 00:13:30.860
Here, have a seat.

00:13:31.620 --> 00:13:32.460
Is soda water okay?

00:13:32.460 --> 00:13:33.340
Yeah.

00:13:35.500 --> 00:13:37.420
I rushed here after work.

00:13:37.420 --> 00:13:38.700
Mingzhu said you guys
had something to discuss.

00:13:38.700 --> 00:13:39.380
What is it?

00:13:39.380 --> 00:13:40.660
We do have something to discuss.

00:13:41.020 --> 00:13:41.740
It's important.

00:13:42.260 --> 00:13:43.260
It's her wedding.

00:13:44.580 --> 00:13:47.420
This is our future sister-in-law,

00:13:47.420 --> 00:13:48.020
Bichen.

00:13:48.220 --> 00:13:48.900
Hello, Dr. Li.

00:13:48.900 --> 00:13:49.860
Hello.

00:13:51.220 --> 00:13:52.100
We met before.

00:13:52.520 --> 00:13:54.340
What's wrong? Was she unable
to receive my consultation?

00:13:54.340 --> 00:13:56.050
Not at all. It's easy
to receive your consultation.

00:13:56.260 --> 00:13:58.500
Look at her.
She doesn't even let me brag.

00:13:58.500 --> 00:13:59.860
You may go ahead.

00:14:00.180 --> 00:14:01.180
It's like this.

00:14:01.940 --> 00:14:03.180
Bichen and my brother

00:14:03.180 --> 00:14:04.500
will get married soon.

00:14:04.500 --> 00:14:07.220
Therefore, we wish to invite you

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:08.500
to hold down their fort.

00:14:08.660 --> 00:14:09.700
Hold down their fort?

00:14:09.980 --> 00:14:12.100
That is to host their wedding.

00:14:12.100 --> 00:14:12.860
Host their wedding?

00:14:13.320 --> 00:14:14.900
Aren't you the poster child
for the art stream?

00:14:14.900 --> 00:14:16.460
I was merely bragging.

00:14:16.460 --> 00:14:17.620
Didn't you host your school's

00:14:17.620 --> 00:14:18.540
100th year anniversary celebration?

00:14:18.540 --> 00:14:19.820
There were over 10 hosts there.

00:14:19.820 --> 00:14:20.940
I stood at the very edge.

00:14:20.940 --> 00:14:21.580
I can't do it.

00:14:22.180 --> 00:14:23.940
Dr. Li, please don't be modest.

00:14:23.940 --> 00:14:27.060
We've already seen your achievements
on the People's Hospital's website.

00:14:27.300 --> 00:14:28.180
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

00:14:28.180 --> 00:14:30.460
You've been hosting
their annual meeting every year.

00:14:30.760 --> 00:14:33.380
Dr. Li, I truly think Nanzhou has plenty of
talented individuals,

00:14:33.380 --> 00:14:35.100
just like you.

00:14:35.100 --> 00:14:35.740
Dr. Li.

00:14:36.540 --> 00:14:39.820
It's not an exaggeration to call you
the top dog at People's Hospital, right?

00:14:39.820 --> 00:14:41.220
Miss, that's over-exaggerating it.

00:14:42.740 --> 00:14:44.420
You guys are buying me a meal

00:14:44.420 --> 00:14:46.060
and buttering me up together.

00:14:46.280 --> 00:14:48.380
It's obvious
that I can't just refuse your request.

00:14:48.390 --> 00:14:49.860
If so, I suppose that's a yes, then.

00:14:51.020 --> 00:14:52.220
Thank you, Dr. Li.

00:14:53.060 --> 00:14:53.940
- Stop.
- Thank you.

00:14:53.940 --> 00:14:56.020
Dr. Li, you're truly multi-talented.

00:14:56.020 --> 00:14:57.540
You're both virtuous and talented.

00:14:57.700 --> 00:15:00.100
I'll say this first.

00:15:00.100 --> 00:15:02.170
It's just like a briefing I do
before any surgery.

00:15:02.420 --> 00:15:04.100
After all, I'm not a professional.

00:15:04.100 --> 00:15:06.380
You may encounter
the following situations.

00:15:06.380 --> 00:15:08.820
Firstly, I might forget the script
when I get too nervous.

00:15:08.820 --> 00:15:09.900
Therefore, at that moment,

00:15:10.140 --> 00:15:11.980
I need the mood-makers to help me out.

00:15:11.980 --> 00:15:12.580
I'll do it.

00:15:13.020 --> 00:15:15.620
Great. Secondly, I might go on for too long
when I get excited.

00:15:15.620 --> 00:15:16.380
Please forgive me for that.

00:15:16.380 --> 00:15:17.500
That's fine. I'll be around.

00:15:17.660 --> 00:15:18.860
Okay. Thirdly,

00:15:18.860 --> 00:15:20.580
if I accept any urgent calls

00:15:20.580 --> 00:15:21.940
from the ER,

00:15:21.940 --> 00:15:23.620
I'll stop the hosting immediately.

00:15:23.620 --> 00:15:24.740
You guys have to prepare a backup plan.

00:15:24.740 --> 00:15:25.460
Dr. Li,

00:15:25.820 --> 00:15:27.260
we're clear with

00:15:27.260 --> 00:15:28.820
every one of your situations.

00:15:29.820 --> 00:15:32.020
Should we sign a pre-hosting agreement?

00:15:32.020 --> 00:15:32.860
It's fine. No need for that.

00:15:32.860 --> 00:15:34.060
That'll be unnecessary.

00:15:34.060 --> 00:15:35.140
We can chat while we eat.

00:15:35.140 --> 00:15:35.660
Okay.

00:15:36.060 --> 00:15:36.700
Dr. Li.

00:15:36.700 --> 00:15:38.460
Here. Warm your belly with some soup.

00:15:38.460 --> 00:15:38.940
Okay. Thank you.

00:15:38.940 --> 00:15:40.780
- You've been busy the entire day.
- Okay.

00:15:40.980 --> 00:15:42.340
My bowl is already full.

00:15:42.580 --> 00:15:44.500
So, why did you guys

00:15:44.500 --> 00:15:45.700
want me to be the host?

00:15:45.700 --> 00:15:47.980
It's because Mingzhu
strongly recommended you.

00:15:48.260 --> 00:15:50.340
Although we're friends,

00:15:50.780 --> 00:15:52.660
I do have high respect for you.

00:15:52.980 --> 00:15:53.940
Do you still remember?

00:15:53.940 --> 00:15:55.140
When I had a cornual pregnancy,

00:15:55.140 --> 00:15:56.660
I was truly afraid back then.

00:15:56.660 --> 00:15:58.100
But you kept consoling me.

00:15:58.500 --> 00:15:59.700
Zhixia's mother did the same.

00:15:59.700 --> 00:16:02.180
You were the one who saved me
when I was bleeding profusely.

00:16:02.180 --> 00:16:02.900
I was just doing my duty.

00:16:02.900 --> 00:16:04.940
To us ordinary folks,

00:16:05.100 --> 00:16:07.500
doctors like you all are our guardians.

00:16:08.260 --> 00:16:09.340
I no longer have the chance.

00:16:09.580 --> 00:16:10.580
If I did have the chance,

00:16:10.580 --> 00:16:12.250
I would've liked for you
to host my wedding as well.

00:16:14.260 --> 00:16:15.980
The love journey
of Bichen and my brother

00:16:15.980 --> 00:16:17.420
was pretty difficult as well.

00:16:17.420 --> 00:16:19.100
Now, everything has settled down.

00:16:19.100 --> 00:16:21.700
Therefore, Dr. Li,
we hope that you can host their wedding.

00:16:21.700 --> 00:16:23.130
And our baby's 100th-day celebration.

00:16:23.140 --> 00:16:24.180
And their baby's
first birthday celebration.

00:16:24.180 --> 00:16:26.020
Why don't you host
the baby's wedding as well?

00:16:26.030 --> 00:16:27.100
I suppose I would be venerable

00:16:27.100 --> 00:16:28.340
and highly respected back then.

00:16:28.340 --> 00:16:29.980
By then, it'll be hard
to receive your consultation.

00:16:29.980 --> 00:16:31.720
Wait, do I still need
to work at that time?

00:16:31.780 --> 00:16:32.740
Come.

00:16:32.740 --> 00:16:34.660
Let's drink tea instead of liquor.

00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:35.180
Alright.

00:16:35.340 --> 00:16:38.140
To the well-respected
and venerable Dr. Li!

00:16:38.140 --> 00:16:38.660
Alright!

00:16:38.660 --> 00:16:40.460
May you do well in your career!

00:16:40.460 --> 00:16:41.960
Alright. I'll also do my best

00:16:41.960 --> 00:16:43.860
to give the newlywed couple
the perfect wedding.

00:16:43.860 --> 00:16:45.100
Thank you.

00:16:48.060 --> 00:16:49.900
I think this package is pretty good.

00:16:49.900 --> 00:16:51.220
(Bridal Package)
It has a complimentary luxury suite too.

00:16:51.500 --> 00:16:53.460
It's still too expensive.

00:16:56.980 --> 00:16:57.740
Miss Feng,

00:16:57.980 --> 00:17:00.220
can we get a discount?

00:17:01.230 --> 00:17:03.500
This package is already
the most thoughtful bridal package

00:17:03.500 --> 00:17:05.220
offered by our hotel.

00:17:05.480 --> 00:17:07.380
We also provide a lot of
complimentary packages.

00:17:07.380 --> 00:17:08.540
It's worth the experience.

00:17:09.820 --> 00:17:10.700
Give us a discount.

00:17:10.710 --> 00:17:12.480
We're hosting a banquet
for 200 people here.

00:17:14.060 --> 00:17:15.580
If so, I'll request the hotel

00:17:16.020 --> 00:17:17.100
to give you guys a bottle of

00:17:17.100 --> 00:17:19.060
complimentary French champagne
worth 888 yuan.

00:17:19.060 --> 00:17:19.660
How about it?

00:17:20.140 --> 00:17:20.980
What do you think?

00:17:21.820 --> 00:17:23.180
The champagne isn't worth it.

00:17:24.460 --> 00:17:26.300
Why don't you give us

00:17:26.300 --> 00:17:27.900
a 888-yuan discount directly?

00:17:28.940 --> 00:17:30.020
Mister, I'm sorry.

00:17:30.020 --> 00:17:31.420
That won't do.

00:17:31.420 --> 00:17:32.940
Why not?

00:17:32.940 --> 00:17:34.730
Just try to apply for it
with your superiors.

00:17:34.740 --> 00:17:35.700
Try asking them.

00:17:35.980 --> 00:17:38.020
My superiors have already
gotten off work.

00:17:38.020 --> 00:17:39.620
You guys are in the service industry.

00:17:39.620 --> 00:17:41.140
To think that you guys
have fixed working hours.

00:17:41.280 --> 00:17:43.550
Even a machine needs to recharge
their batteries, you know?

00:17:43.940 --> 00:17:45.100
What attitude is that?

00:17:45.900 --> 00:17:47.460
Is this how your hotel does business?

00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:50.140
You guys are belittling us just because

00:17:50.150 --> 00:17:52.250
we're inquiring about
the cheapest bridal package, huh?

00:17:53.500 --> 00:17:54.980
Dear, let's find another place.

00:17:55.220 --> 00:17:56.500
We won't do business with them.

00:17:56.780 --> 00:17:57.540
Let's go.

00:17:59.420 --> 00:18:00.140
Take the coffee.

00:18:03.820 --> 00:18:04.460
Meiqi.

00:18:05.420 --> 00:18:05.860
Wait.

00:18:07.260 --> 00:18:09.100
How is it? Did you clinch the deal?

00:18:10.140 --> 00:18:10.820
No, I didn't.

00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:12.320
They thought it was too expensive.

00:18:13.700 --> 00:18:15.660
You have to explain it to the clients.

00:18:15.660 --> 00:18:16.980
Our services are expensive for a reason.

00:18:16.980 --> 00:18:18.460
I've already explained
everything I needed to.

00:18:18.460 --> 00:18:20.040
They still thought it was too expensive.

00:18:21.340 --> 00:18:21.940
Meiqi,

00:18:22.860 --> 00:18:24.910
everyone knows
that you come from a well-off family.

00:18:25.100 --> 00:18:27.220
It's like you don't care
about your commission at all

00:18:27.320 --> 00:18:28.660
But I hope you'll understand this.

00:18:29.180 --> 00:18:32.420
You can only do a good job
if you care about the job.

00:18:35.340 --> 00:18:36.300
I heard that Nanxi Hotel

00:18:36.300 --> 00:18:38.100
has taken away
a lot of our business lately.

00:18:38.100 --> 00:18:40.260
I heard that the retro bridal banquet

00:18:40.900 --> 00:18:43.300
created by two of their female employees
was all the craze.

00:18:44.020 --> 00:18:44.660
Meiqi,

00:18:45.620 --> 00:18:47.740
you're an elite graduate
who came back from overseas.

00:18:48.450 --> 00:18:49.860
You should put more effort into it.

00:18:50.860 --> 00:18:52.340
If you don't hit this season's KPI,

00:18:53.340 --> 00:18:54.740
we'll get us in trouble.

00:18:59.900 --> 00:19:00.820
Your shrimp is ready.

00:19:00.820 --> 00:19:01.420
Please enjoy your meal.

00:19:01.420 --> 00:19:02.460
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

00:19:03.900 --> 00:19:04.500
Dr. Li,

00:19:04.820 --> 00:19:07.060
once we're done with Bichen's wedding,

00:19:07.060 --> 00:19:08.980
I'll do my best
to find you a girlfriend.

00:19:08.980 --> 00:19:09.620
No thanks.

00:19:09.620 --> 00:19:10.980
Were you single all this time?

00:19:11.380 --> 00:19:12.350
I once had a girlfriend.

00:19:12.820 --> 00:19:14.460
Dr. Li is a golden bachelor.

00:19:14.620 --> 00:19:15.780
I'm famous for being single.

00:19:15.980 --> 00:19:16.660
Don't worry.

00:19:16.980 --> 00:19:18.780
That'll change once I help him out.

00:19:19.160 --> 00:19:19.900
Miss, no need for that.

00:19:19.900 --> 00:19:21.580
I think I'm leading a carefree life

00:19:21.820 --> 00:19:22.900
as a single man.

00:19:22.900 --> 00:19:23.740
Once I marry someone,

00:19:23.740 --> 00:19:25.300
I'll gain a lot of new relatives.

00:19:25.640 --> 00:19:27.060
Life is already troublesome enough.

00:19:27.060 --> 00:19:28.940
If I do so, it'll only make
my life more troublesome.

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:30.300
Everyone here is
a relative of one another.

00:19:30.300 --> 00:19:31.580
I'll ask you for a favor,
and you'll ask me for a favor.

00:19:31.580 --> 00:19:32.580
Isn't that fun?

00:19:33.780 --> 00:19:34.700
Don't take it for real.

00:19:34.700 --> 00:19:36.340
Zhixia was just joking with you.

00:19:36.580 --> 00:19:38.220
You can live however you want to live.

00:19:38.220 --> 00:19:38.820
Alright.

00:19:38.980 --> 00:19:40.580
Here, have some shrimp.

00:19:46.220 --> 00:19:46.980
What's the matter?

00:19:50.680 --> 00:19:52.380
This is the first time
someone has peeled my shrimp from me

00:19:52.380 --> 00:19:53.820
since I was a child.

00:20:22.340 --> 00:20:23.060
Meiqi.

00:20:23.580 --> 00:20:24.180
Mom?

00:20:24.580 --> 00:20:25.500
What's the matter?

00:20:26.500 --> 00:20:27.900
I was looking at you from above.

00:20:27.900 --> 00:20:29.220
You've been sitting here
for a while now.

00:20:29.220 --> 00:20:30.380
Why didn't you come upstairs?

00:20:32.020 --> 00:20:32.780
And,

00:20:33.220 --> 00:20:35.340
why didn't you drive to work today?

00:20:38.160 --> 00:20:40.100
I was quite tired.
I didn't feel like driving.

00:20:42.700 --> 00:20:44.540
Are you upset with something?

00:20:46.140 --> 00:20:48.180
That's not it. You see...

00:20:49.720 --> 00:20:52.500
The sales performance of our hotel's
current season isn't looking good.

00:20:52.980 --> 00:20:54.420
My boss gave me some pressure.

00:20:55.460 --> 00:20:57.420
But I thought I was
already working hard enough.

00:20:57.420 --> 00:20:59.250
I even worked overtime
to serve additional customers.

00:20:59.260 --> 00:21:00.140
Precisely.

00:21:00.260 --> 00:21:01.460
You came back very late.

00:21:02.340 --> 00:21:04.740
And, I couldn't hit my KPI

00:21:04.740 --> 00:21:06.940
because the people of Nanzhou
don't like to spend money.

00:21:07.260 --> 00:21:09.380
The couple I served today thought
our packages were expensive too.

00:21:09.380 --> 00:21:10.350
Bichen thought the same.

00:21:11.500 --> 00:21:14.160
It's impossible to communicate
when our perceptions are different.

00:21:16.100 --> 00:21:17.220
Silly girl,

00:21:17.220 --> 00:21:18.940
were you upset over this?

00:21:19.220 --> 00:21:21.180
I told you long ago.

00:21:21.180 --> 00:21:23.380
You could quit
if you're unhappy with your job.

00:21:23.380 --> 00:21:25.340
Our family doesn't
need your wage anyway.

00:21:25.980 --> 00:21:26.580
Mom.

00:21:27.500 --> 00:21:28.220
Meiqi?

00:21:28.220 --> 00:21:29.540
What are you guys doing here?

00:21:29.540 --> 00:21:30.100
Mingzhu,

00:21:30.100 --> 00:21:31.740
why did you come back this late?

00:21:31.740 --> 00:21:33.500
A friend of mine was pregnant too.

00:21:33.700 --> 00:21:35.780
I took her out to have a meal
with Dr. Li today.

00:21:35.780 --> 00:21:36.700
Dr. Li?

00:21:41.860 --> 00:21:42.540
Mingzhu,

00:21:43.140 --> 00:21:44.620
this is a reminder.

00:21:45.260 --> 00:21:47.940
You're pregnant with the grandchild of
the Feng family, you know?

00:21:49.620 --> 00:21:50.220
Mom.

00:21:51.140 --> 00:21:51.540
Mom,

00:21:52.040 --> 00:21:53.640
you're kicking a huge fuss over nothing.

00:21:53.660 --> 00:21:54.620
She just went out to socialize.

00:21:54.620 --> 00:21:56.650
It has nothing to do
with whose child she's pregnant with.

00:21:56.900 --> 00:21:58.140
What are you saying?

00:21:58.840 --> 00:22:00.860
We sent you to England
for your studies, you know?

00:22:00.860 --> 00:22:02.820
Were such twisted values
all you've learned over there?

00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:04.420
Mom, that's not it.

00:22:04.420 --> 00:22:06.780
Values aren't decided by
your preferences alone.

00:22:07.060 --> 00:22:09.020
Yes, I did go to England
to see the world.

00:22:09.020 --> 00:22:10.100
I did broaden my horizons.

00:22:10.100 --> 00:22:10.940
But in the end?

00:22:10.940 --> 00:22:13.040
I still had no choice
but to stay cooped up in Nanzhou.

00:22:13.060 --> 00:22:14.300
I had to work under pressure
even during overtime shifts.

00:22:14.300 --> 00:22:16.200
And, I might be making less money
than Hu Gang.

00:22:16.220 --> 00:22:18.140
Are you saying
that we're dragging you down?

00:22:20.420 --> 00:22:21.220
I didn't say that.

00:22:21.220 --> 00:22:22.340
If so, what were you implying, then?

00:22:22.340 --> 00:22:23.900
What's wrong with coming back?
Is it bad to come back?

00:22:23.900 --> 00:22:25.300
I think it's great.

00:22:25.740 --> 00:22:27.300
You have everything you need at home.

00:22:27.300 --> 00:22:29.220
And, we know Hu Gang inside out.

00:22:29.220 --> 00:22:30.620
He's a good potential partner for you.

00:22:30.620 --> 00:22:31.380
He's good for you in every way.

00:22:31.380 --> 00:22:32.860
Who said so? He's bad for me in every way!

00:22:32.860 --> 00:22:33.540
Meiqi,

00:22:33.780 --> 00:22:34.860
stop it.

00:22:35.780 --> 00:22:37.140
Mom has a point.

00:22:37.140 --> 00:22:38.700
Are you serious?

00:22:38.700 --> 00:22:39.660
I was speaking up for you.

00:22:39.660 --> 00:22:41.060
Can you have some spine for once?

00:22:41.060 --> 00:22:43.020
Don't you understand what Mom
was trying to imply?

00:22:43.020 --> 00:22:44.260
She even said I had twisted values.

00:22:44.260 --> 00:22:45.380
Who said her values weren't twisted?

00:22:45.380 --> 00:22:46.780
What did I say?

00:22:47.300 --> 00:22:48.660
What did you mean by that?

00:22:49.860 --> 00:22:51.180
Do you know what era we're living in?

00:22:51.180 --> 00:22:52.260
Women should be independent now.

00:22:52.260 --> 00:22:53.780
Don't delude yourself into thinking
that you can gain prestige through me.

00:22:53.780 --> 00:22:55.100
What are you saying?

00:22:55.100 --> 00:22:56.060
Feng Meiqi!

00:22:56.060 --> 00:22:56.860
Stop right there!

00:22:56.860 --> 00:22:57.420
Mom.

00:22:58.340 --> 00:22:59.620
That's how Meiqi is.

00:22:59.630 --> 00:23:00.740
A strong independent woman.

00:23:00.740 --> 00:23:01.860
Strong independent woman?

00:23:01.860 --> 00:23:03.580
She's just spoiled by her father.

00:23:05.060 --> 00:23:05.940
And you,

00:23:06.500 --> 00:23:08.900
you're pregnant now.

00:23:09.220 --> 00:23:11.380
You shouldn't
wear yourself out like that.

00:23:11.540 --> 00:23:12.620
But I feel fine.

