00:34:03.340 --> 00:34:04.300
Initially,

00:34:05.620 --> 00:34:06.380
I didn't.

00:34:07.980 --> 00:34:08.820
However,

00:34:09.620 --> 00:34:11.060
after today's meal,

00:34:13.740 --> 00:34:15.020
I don't think that's a huge deal.

00:34:18.180 --> 00:34:19.020
You brat.

00:34:24.500 --> 00:34:27.220
If so, your uncle's acting
was pretty convincing.

00:34:28.620 --> 00:34:30.340
He's very prideful.
Don't expose him, okay?

00:34:33.660 --> 00:34:36.620
The bride's father will
hold his daughter's hand

00:34:36.620 --> 00:34:38.540
and walk toward the groom slowly.

00:34:38.820 --> 00:34:40.260
Groom, slow down.

00:34:40.420 --> 00:34:41.420
I know you're impatient,

00:34:41.420 --> 00:34:42.750
but you aren't going to work here.

00:34:44.020 --> 00:34:46.300
Walk toward each other slowly.

00:34:49.380 --> 00:34:50.740
Maintain your smile.

00:34:53.660 --> 00:34:54.860
The bride's father will

00:34:54.860 --> 00:34:57.580
hand his daughter's hand to the groom.

00:34:59.500 --> 00:35:00.260
Xu Zhidong.

00:35:01.480 --> 00:35:02.780
You'd better be nice to Bichen.

00:35:02.980 --> 00:35:04.120
If not, I won't let you off.

00:35:06.680 --> 00:35:07.340
Extend your arm.

00:35:08.360 --> 00:35:09.700
Do you actually think
that you're her father?

00:35:09.700 --> 00:35:10.460
I am!

00:35:11.380 --> 00:35:12.020
Alright.

00:35:12.020 --> 00:35:14.540
You two may now exchange your vows.

00:35:14.860 --> 00:35:16.060
Our vows?

00:35:16.300 --> 00:35:17.260
What should I say?

00:35:17.780 --> 00:35:18.540
What should we say?

00:35:19.740 --> 00:35:20.980
Getting married is so tiring.

00:35:20.980 --> 00:35:22.060
Even my back is sweaty.

00:35:22.220 --> 00:35:23.340
How was our performance?

00:35:24.020 --> 00:35:25.060
- Come.
- He was terrible.

00:35:25.060 --> 00:35:25.620
Bride.

00:35:25.620 --> 00:35:27.020
Come, I'll touch up on your makeup.

00:35:27.340 --> 00:35:29.780
When the lighting hits you,
your lipstick won't be visible.

00:35:29.780 --> 00:35:31.020
We need to apply more lipstick to you.

00:35:31.020 --> 00:35:32.540
And, we need to fix your brows too.

00:35:32.860 --> 00:35:33.820
You're so professional.

00:35:34.820 --> 00:35:35.700
Bichen, are you tired?

00:35:35.700 --> 00:35:36.700
Is the baby reacting?

00:35:36.860 --> 00:35:38.020
Not for now.

00:35:38.020 --> 00:35:39.180
I just feel sleepy all the time.

00:35:39.180 --> 00:35:40.700
That's normal. I feel sleepy too.

00:35:41.860 --> 00:35:43.740
What does the groom need to do, then?

00:35:43.740 --> 00:35:45.060
Nothing. You just need to rest.

00:35:46.820 --> 00:35:47.380
Manager,

00:35:48.340 --> 00:35:49.340
take a look.

00:35:51.760 --> 00:35:53.140
We've finished all the decoration

00:35:53.140 --> 00:35:55.140
as per this blueprint.

00:35:55.700 --> 00:35:56.500
Have some water.

00:35:56.860 --> 00:35:57.980
Thank you.

00:35:58.620 --> 00:36:00.140
You may leave first if you're busy.

00:36:00.140 --> 00:36:01.620
I don't think I'll be done that quickly.

00:36:01.620 --> 00:36:02.500
I'm free anyway.

00:36:02.780 --> 00:36:04.540
Don't you need to
go on a date with Mr. Hu?

00:36:05.080 --> 00:36:06.980
He's unromantic.
I couldn't care less about him.

00:36:07.795 --> 00:36:09.675
If so, you should educate him.

00:36:09.700 --> 00:36:10.900
Why should I?

00:36:10.900 --> 00:36:12.340
He can learn by himself.

00:36:21.860 --> 00:36:22.980
Turn around. Let me see.

00:36:26.260 --> 00:36:28.220
I think a light and elegant makeup style

00:36:28.220 --> 00:36:29.620
suits Bichen better.

00:36:30.960 --> 00:36:32.660
The first set she'll wear
is their wedding attire.

00:36:32.660 --> 00:36:33.820
Light makeup isn't appropriate.

00:36:33.820 --> 00:36:35.780
Look at all the fancy decorations.

00:36:35.780 --> 00:36:37.860
We have to emphasize her radiance.

00:36:39.820 --> 00:36:41.500
Nanzhou is a small place indeed.

00:36:42.250 --> 00:36:44.140
The makeup of newlywed couples
are too thick.

00:36:44.140 --> 00:36:45.050
It's not classy at all.

00:36:46.300 --> 00:36:48.260
Do you guys usually go out
for further training?

00:36:48.260 --> 00:36:50.260
For example, to France, Korea, or so on?

00:36:50.260 --> 00:36:51.850
We usually go to Tieling
for further training.

00:36:52.860 --> 00:36:54.460
Actually, I think it's fine.

00:36:54.460 --> 00:36:56.100
My parents like bright red makeup.

00:37:02.380 --> 00:37:03.540
This is such a festive color.

00:37:04.220 --> 00:37:05.420
It's my first time trying this.

00:37:05.660 --> 00:37:06.220
Yeah, right?

00:37:06.360 --> 00:37:07.350
It does look good on you.

00:37:11.360 --> 00:37:13.860
Manager, I think there's something wrong
with the PA system.

00:37:14.380 --> 00:37:15.100
Let me see.

00:37:15.380 --> 00:37:16.540
Go and switch it off first.

00:37:16.540 --> 00:37:17.380
- Yeah, switch it off first.
- Okay.

00:37:17.380 --> 00:37:19.580
I guess it's a contact issue.

00:37:19.580 --> 00:37:20.620
Let me check.

00:37:22.860 --> 00:37:24.300
Is it due to the poor contact?

00:37:24.860 --> 00:37:25.500
Let me see.

00:37:26.180 --> 00:37:27.140
This shouldn't be.

00:37:27.140 --> 00:37:27.860
I told you already.

00:37:27.860 --> 00:37:28.740
Is it an issue with the circuit?

00:37:28.740 --> 00:37:29.860
You shouldn't be frugal
when it comes to your wedding.

00:37:29.860 --> 00:37:30.980
I can't resolve this issue.

00:37:30.980 --> 00:37:32.350
We have to find
the maintenance department.

00:37:33.180 --> 00:37:35.140
It's lunch hour for the technicians now.

00:37:35.140 --> 00:37:36.060
That's fine.

00:37:36.060 --> 00:37:37.950
We don't need music, then.
I'll take it as a compromise.

00:37:38.020 --> 00:37:39.180
How can you compromise?

00:37:39.380 --> 00:37:41.060
It's your wedding. It should be perfect.

00:37:41.060 --> 00:37:42.090
We shouldn't compromise.

00:37:42.100 --> 00:37:44.180
No problem. It's not a huge issue.

00:37:45.040 --> 00:37:46.560
I'll hire someone to fix it for you.

00:37:46.660 --> 00:37:47.700
Will you call for Hu Gang?

00:37:48.860 --> 00:37:49.940
No need for that, Meiqi.

00:37:49.940 --> 00:37:51.780
Our technician will come back
at 1:30 P.M.

00:37:52.020 --> 00:37:53.530
It's fine. Mingzhu, you have no idea.

00:37:53.540 --> 00:37:54.940
Hu Gang was waiting for
Meiqi to call him.

00:37:54.940 --> 00:37:56.300
This way, he'll have an out.

00:37:56.660 --> 00:37:58.380
I'm sure he'll come later.

00:38:02.020 --> 00:38:04.140
(Meiqi)

00:38:08.700 --> 00:38:09.940
(Meiqi)

00:38:12.860 --> 00:38:13.380
Hello?

00:38:13.380 --> 00:38:14.380
Hello, Mr. Hu.

00:38:14.380 --> 00:38:15.700
What took you so long?

00:38:16.700 --> 00:38:17.540
Listen.

00:38:17.760 --> 00:38:20.460
My best friend is going through her
wedding rehearsal at Nanxi Hotel now.

00:38:20.460 --> 00:38:22.330
But there's something wrong
with the PA system.

00:38:22.340 --> 00:38:23.780
Come here and fix it.

00:38:24.860 --> 00:38:27.020
What seems to be the issue?

00:38:27.380 --> 00:38:30.140
Is it just static noise?
Or is it a screech?

00:38:30.380 --> 00:38:31.900
How would I know?

00:38:31.900 --> 00:38:32.580
Meiqi,

00:38:32.740 --> 00:38:34.020
I'll explain it to Mr. Hu.

00:38:34.180 --> 00:38:35.160
I'll explain it to him.

00:38:36.860 --> 00:38:37.860
Hello, Mr. Hu?

00:38:38.180 --> 00:38:39.140
I'm Mingzhu.

00:38:39.420 --> 00:38:41.100
Sorry for the trouble.

00:38:41.380 --> 00:38:42.060
It's like this.

00:38:42.060 --> 00:38:44.860
The PA equipment we rented for
Ni Wedding Planning

00:38:45.660 --> 00:38:46.860
is quite dated.

00:38:49.620 --> 00:38:50.620
Ni Wedding Planning?

00:38:51.260 --> 00:38:51.860
Yeah.

00:38:52.220 --> 00:38:54.060
Since you're in the
wedding-planning industry,

00:38:54.070 --> 00:38:56.160
the equipment really has to be
upgraded and updated.

00:38:56.180 --> 00:38:57.410
What if something goes wrong

00:38:57.410 --> 00:38:58.210
- during the wedding?
- Okay.

00:38:58.220 --> 00:38:59.820
The newlywed will regret it
for the rest of their lives.

00:38:59.820 --> 00:39:01.740
If something goes wrong,
we can just fix it.

00:39:01.740 --> 00:39:03.020
You're already looking for help
as we speak.

00:39:03.020 --> 00:39:04.100
What if I can't find any help?

00:39:04.100 --> 00:39:05.100
How could that be?

00:39:05.100 --> 00:39:06.100
You already called him personally.

00:39:06.100 --> 00:39:07.380
I'm sure he would come.

00:39:08.820 --> 00:39:09.500
Meiqi,

00:39:09.900 --> 00:39:12.300
Mr. Hu is tutoring the students now.

00:39:12.300 --> 00:39:13.660
He won't be able to come for now.

00:39:26.180 --> 00:39:26.780
Hu Gang.

00:39:27.620 --> 00:39:28.940
Are you sure you're not free?

00:39:28.940 --> 00:39:30.220
Are you sure about that?

00:39:35.660 --> 00:39:36.660
You'd better think twice.

00:39:39.020 --> 00:39:40.860
Senior year teachers are always busy.

00:39:40.860 --> 00:39:42.380
The NCEE is a huge deal, you know?

00:39:42.700 --> 00:39:44.660
Yeah.
I'm sure Mr. Hu is anxious about it too.

00:39:44.660 --> 00:39:46.060
It's impossible to be filial
and loyal at the same time.

00:39:46.060 --> 00:39:47.340
What nonsense is that?

00:39:47.350 --> 00:39:49.380
I'm not his mother.
Why should he be filial to me?

00:39:52.020 --> 00:39:54.220
I have a report to hand in
this afternoon.

00:39:54.220 --> 00:39:55.160
I'll make a move first.

00:39:55.540 --> 00:39:56.420
You should go ahead.

00:39:56.420 --> 00:39:57.220
You guys can continue.

00:39:57.220 --> 00:39:57.740
Goodbye.

00:39:58.020 --> 00:39:59.380
Goodbye.

00:39:59.620 --> 00:40:01.740
Get rid of your lousy equipment
as soon as possible.

00:40:02.180 --> 00:40:02.700
Sure.

00:40:02.700 --> 00:40:05.040
You should expand your poor connections
as soon as possible too.

00:40:05.820 --> 00:40:07.020
What are you laughing at?

00:40:07.460 --> 00:40:08.700
You want the issue to blow up?

00:40:08.700 --> 00:40:09.700
What are you laughing at?

00:40:10.020 --> 00:40:12.100
Your sister-in-law is so mean.

00:40:12.100 --> 00:40:13.300
Only you guys can tolerate her.

00:40:13.980 --> 00:40:15.580
Meiqi led a pampered life since young.

00:40:15.580 --> 00:40:16.620
She's pretty willful.

00:40:16.620 --> 00:40:17.700
But she's quite nice.

00:40:17.700 --> 00:40:20.320
Yeah. She came to my rehearsal
when she heard that I needed help.

00:40:20.330 --> 00:40:21.540
I would rather she didn't come.

00:40:21.540 --> 00:40:22.340
When she's here,

00:40:22.580 --> 00:40:24.260
we have to serve her like a mistress.

00:40:24.260 --> 00:40:25.500
That's because
you feel guilty toward her.

00:40:25.500 --> 00:40:25.980
I...

00:40:26.860 --> 00:40:28.420
But we have to remind her

00:40:28.420 --> 00:40:29.660
that she's just a bridesmaid.

00:40:29.960 --> 00:40:31.980
What if she gets infuriated
during the wedding?

00:40:32.380 --> 00:40:32.980
Yeah.

00:40:33.620 --> 00:40:35.340
What should we do if she causes trouble

00:40:35.340 --> 00:40:36.100
during our wedding?

00:40:36.240 --> 00:40:37.180
There's nothing to worry about.

00:40:37.180 --> 00:40:38.300
I'm here, aren't I?

00:40:38.500 --> 00:40:39.860
I can do what Meiqi can do.

00:40:39.860 --> 00:40:41.700
I can even do what she cannot.

00:40:41.700 --> 00:40:43.220
Stop fanning the flames.

00:40:43.220 --> 00:40:44.380
I'm not.

00:40:44.380 --> 00:40:45.980
I'm just making a statement here.

00:40:50.020 --> 00:40:50.660
Hu Gang.

00:40:51.020 --> 00:40:52.540
All clear at Nanxi Hotel.

00:40:52.540 --> 00:40:53.680
Come as soon as possible.

00:40:55.620 --> 00:40:56.220
Who?

00:40:56.820 --> 00:40:57.540
Hu Gang?

00:41:00.560 --> 00:41:01.060
You two...

00:41:01.660 --> 00:41:02.980
That's right. It's us now.

00:41:06.020 --> 00:41:06.540
Meiqi,

00:41:06.860 --> 00:41:07.980
I sent you the marketing plan

00:41:07.980 --> 00:41:09.980
from last Thanksgiving.

00:41:10.220 --> 00:41:12.380
Modify it and make one
for this year's Thanksgiving.

00:41:12.740 --> 00:41:14.060
You have to be detailed.

00:41:14.100 --> 00:41:15.700
Do it immediately. I need it urgently.

00:41:16.660 --> 00:41:17.860
Got it, Samantha.

00:41:31.420 --> 00:41:33.820
It seems Mr. Hu doesn't have the guts
to refuse me after all.

00:41:37.820 --> 00:41:38.500
Mr. Hu,

00:41:38.500 --> 00:41:39.380
I think it's fixed.

00:41:39.380 --> 00:41:40.140
Is there sound now?

00:41:40.140 --> 00:41:41.950
Hear it and
see if there's any static noise.

00:41:42.260 --> 00:41:43.140
Nope.

00:41:43.140 --> 00:41:43.940
Nope, huh?

00:41:47.060 --> 00:41:47.660
All done.

00:41:49.380 --> 00:41:49.980
Mr. Hu,

00:41:49.980 --> 00:41:51.180
thank you for coming today.

00:41:51.180 --> 00:41:52.060
You're such a professional.

00:41:52.060 --> 00:41:53.220
Even the technicians

00:41:53.220 --> 00:41:54.380
might not be able to fix this.

00:41:55.060 --> 00:41:56.940
This is an issue with
the transmission cable.

00:41:56.940 --> 00:41:59.420
It's because the console
is too far away from the sound system.

00:41:59.420 --> 00:42:00.740
It'll be fine once you change it

00:42:00.740 --> 00:42:01.550
to a balanced input.

00:42:02.180 --> 00:42:02.980
Thank you, Mr. Hu.

00:42:03.340 --> 00:42:05.540
Not only is Mr. Hu intelligent,

00:42:05.540 --> 00:42:07.140
but he's also very handy.

00:42:07.320 --> 00:42:08.860
Here. A preserved plum as your reward.

00:42:09.900 --> 00:42:10.660
It's your reward.

00:42:10.980 --> 00:42:11.660
Isn't it sweet?

00:42:13.340 --> 00:42:13.860
It is.

00:42:13.860 --> 00:42:14.420
Isn't it?

00:42:15.980 --> 00:42:18.180
Did Mr. Hu have a relationship
with Meiqi before this?

00:42:18.900 --> 00:42:20.380
That's already in the past.

00:42:21.260 --> 00:42:22.620
How did we end up with a love triangle

00:42:22.620 --> 00:42:24.180
on our wedding rehearsal?

00:42:24.180 --> 00:42:25.100
How should I know?

00:42:29.900 --> 00:42:30.460
Hu Gang,

00:42:30.620 --> 00:42:31.660
our home Wi-Fi is down.

00:42:31.860 --> 00:42:33.540
Our Al home system has collapsed.

00:42:33.980 --> 00:42:35.100
Please come and fix it.

00:42:38.340 --> 00:42:39.140
That shouldn't be.

00:42:39.780 --> 00:42:41.660
I installed their Wi-Fi for them.

00:42:41.660 --> 00:42:42.660
It shouldn't be possible.

00:42:55.100 --> 00:42:56.950
The world is noisy

00:42:57.550 --> 00:42:59.930
Turning around,
it's already a distant view

00:43:01.350 --> 00:43:03.230
Once I didnt know what to do

00:43:03.230 --> 00:43:05.310
What to hold quietly

00:43:05.310 --> 00:43:08.260
Like a silent care

00:43:10.120 --> 00:43:12.530
Seasons pass by

00:43:12.530 --> 00:43:15.390
Time ticks away

00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:17.790
Seems like I understand a little

00:43:17.790 --> 00:43:19.570
And also let go of some things

00:43:19.570 --> 00:43:24.290
All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth

00:43:24.290 --> 00:43:27.780
A long letter is written down

00:43:27.930 --> 00:43:31.410
Gently spreading love

00:43:31.610 --> 00:43:35.600
To all the forks in fate

00:43:35.600 --> 00:43:41.230
Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved